@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@adminToken = ...

### ------------------------------------------------------------------------
### ARTICLE & CORPORATE SERVICES (ADMIN & PUBLIC)
### ------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Create Article (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "title": "Top 10 Scholarship Tips",
    "content": "Here are the tips...",
    "category": "scholarship"
}

### List Articles (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles
Accept: application/json

### Submit Corporate Contact (Public Company)
POST {{baseUrl}}/corporate-contact
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Big Tech Company",
    "email": "partnerships@bigtech.com",
    "message": "We want to collaborate on a bootcamp."
}

### List Corporate Contacts (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/corporate-contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json
